    <item>
      <title>美国办公楼危机缓解、信贷改善，加拿大帝国商业银行业绩超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/cibc-beats-estimates-as-us-office-woes-ease-credit-improves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大帝国商业银行的业绩超出分析师预期，因为其拨备低于预期，用于弥补潜在不良贷款，并表示已解决了美国办公室贷款中的大部分问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/cibc-beats-estimates-as-us-office-woes-ease-credit-improves</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 10:27:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Birkenstock 前景未变，令投资者失望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/birkenstock-affirms-outlook-amid-strong-demand-for-sandals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管消费者抢购了更多高端凉鞋和木屐，但 Birkenstock Holding Plc 仍未改变其 2024 年的财务目标，令投资者感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/birkenstock-affirms-outlook-amid-strong-demand-for-sandals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 09:10:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
